### Local Configuration ###
# Keep your API keys and secrets here - never commit this file!
local.properties

### Local operational notes (deploy checklists, scratch pads) ###
# These may contain secrets, hostnames, or env-var values during a
# deploy. Wipe + recreate fresh per deploy.
# Template (DEPLOY_CHECKLIST.template.md) is committed; the working
# copy below is local-only.
DEPLOY_CHECKLIST.md
NOTES.md
SCRATCH.md

### Private docs — never pushed to the public repo ###
# Anything strangers shouldn't read: half-formed plans, personal
# budgets, account/billing details, incident notes. Public docs live
# in docs/; private thinking lives here or in *.private.md anywhere.
docs/private/
*.private.md

.env
.env.*
!.env.example

### Secrets / certs ###
*.pem
*.p12
*.key
*.keystore
*.jks

### Postman exports — usually contain real API keys in Authorization headers ###
# If you want to commit a sanitised version, replace real values with {{apiKey}}
# placeholders first and explicitly `git add -f path/to/file`.
*.postman_collection.json
*.postman_environment.json

